<pc>」</pc>夜攻殺之<pc>，</pc>並監軍史良佐<pc>，</pc>推何進滔為帥以請<pc>，</pc>詔贈憲誠太尉<pc>，</pc>實大和<measure quantity="3" unit="years">
<num value="3">三</num>年</measure>
<pc>。</pc>憲誠起<pc>，</pc>凡<measure quantity="7" unit="years">
<num value="7">七</num>年</measure>
